title.narrative: Strengthening Human Rights Systems in El Salvador
Strengthening Human Rights Systems in El Salvador

description.narrative: La USAID El Salvador proporcionará las intervenciones que protegen contra o responden a los abusos de derechos humanos y fortalecen a las instituciones locales de los derechos humanos, incluyendo la oficina de general del abogado. [CARSI]
USAID/El Salvador will provide interventions that protect against or respond to human rights abuses and strengthen local human rights institutions, including the Attorney General's Office. [CARSI]
